one by one, all the leaders and also certain

00:55:48.913 --> 00:55:54.093
individuals who want to see me.

00:55:54.093 --> 00:56:12.433
We are going to have marriages, and everything,
performed here and it’s going to work out very well.

00:56:12.933 --> 00:56:16.293
