00:56:16.933 --> 00:56:28.313
Do it in your sobriety, in understanding that,
this marriage is nothing but because you have

00:56:28.313 --> 00:56:38.653
to have children of very high quality. Secondly it has to be auspicious.

00:56:40.433 --> 00:56:45.173
Just to wash off if there was any inauspiciousness.

00:56:56.733 --> 00:57:10.853
I hope you will enjoy your heights now, you
will enjoy you glory and you will enjoy your noble work.

00:57:10.853 --> 00:57:12.733
May God bless you.